FBIS4-5387 "dreas069_n_94009" FBIS-EAS-94-069 Daily Report 9 Apr 1994 Vietnam Tourism Agreement Signed With China Tourism Agreement Signed With China BK0904102494 Hanoi VNA in English 0658 GMT 9 Apr 94 BK0904102494 Hanoi VNA English BFN [Text] Hanoi VNA April 9 -- An agreement on tourism cooperation between Vietnam and China was signed here yesterday. Signatories were General Director of the Vietnam National Administration of Tourism [VNAT] Do Quang Trung and General Director of the China General Administration of Travel and Tourism (CGATT) Liu Yi. The signing ceremony was also witnessed by representatives of the Vietnam governmental office and Chinese Ambassador to Vietnam Zhang Qing. Earlier, a delegation of VNAT held talks with a delegation of the CGATT to discuss the cooperation in tourism between the two countries.
